---
title: Middle Eastern Dukkah Beef with Carrot Couscous Salad & Yoghurt
description: Can we have a huzzah for dukkah? We know you’ll be cheering for this delicious number, with a spice that’s fit for this tender beef rump. With the addition of a veggie-filled herby couscous at play, there’s nothing not to love about this easy weeknight supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-dukkah-beef-rump-bb230781.jpg
